{"tid":105153,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[信念哥信念推介] 291 華潤啤酒","createTime":"2017-02-02T16:05:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-08T13:03:11.000Z","uid":81805,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cc565792fad61c83aea4b35d33b0fc33cc1ad269","tid":105153,"uid":81805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T16:05:05.000Z","msg":"係推介股票前 介紹下自己先<br />\n本人 信念哥 相信股票市場暗地裡有一套秩序，只要夠信念，就可以跟住秩序去搵食。<br />\n依套秩序唔包括細價股(俗稱妖股)<br />\n除非你本人非常熟識股票的莊家, 或是大時代的出現 否則長遠來看沉迷細價股蝕比賺多<br />\n<br />\n本人認為炒大價股好處很多 嬴面大很多 遲點各位有興趣 本人可以再分享多一點<br />\n<br />\n2/3/2017 <br />\n信念哥信念推介<br />\n291 華潤啤酒 開市入 睇升10%<br />\n(本人$15.1 已經入左2手)<br />\n只要夠信念 輕鬆賺錢無難道<br />\n<br />\n另外 各位都可以問其他股票或大市問題 有時間我會解答大家"},{"pid":"c3148df1e896c2a61d62edcb6be9565339b9c2b7","tid":105153,"uid":81805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T06:09:06.000Z","msg":"信念一推"},{"pid":"a9fde75fc4da3e5eb50549e02170c5887c53c08c","tid":105153,"uid":8439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T06:25:54.000Z","msg":"無分析架？"},{"pid":"97346225f4de563ac6fdf626f776a3dc12c03d94","tid":105153,"uid":81805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T06:27:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無分析架？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n靠信念"},{"pid":"949d8dfe342b334e81b3d0bd9ba7546063d71a00","tid":105153,"uid":12720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T06:30:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無分析架？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n靠信念</blockquote><br />\n師傅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eef52071573877b26420432206db2cf2ebb96c8d","tid":105153,"uid":8439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T06:31:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無分析架？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n靠信念</blockquote><br />\n屌你老味....我返出去先 打搞曬"},{"pid":"729a1d8473a4a06fb8773f70618adc219ad46bb6","tid":105153,"uid":81805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T06:45:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>無分析架？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n靠信念</blockquote><br />\n屌你老味....我返出去先 打搞曬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n下下都問候人係好無品 炒股好著重人品"},{"pid":"e953ca4d3810af6b630e369bd9428b1607142881","tid":105153,"uid":3539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T06:50:51.000Z","msg":"打算放幾耐？"},{"pid":"d02b61d4977354219d4f4bda75ed1a6e62a15c2f","tid":105153,"uid":81805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T07:06:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打算放幾耐？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一個月內"},{"pid":"feb095fdacd2f06da251c885c80ab554643d4168","tid":105153,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T09:34:15.000Z","msg":"用念力令到股價大升 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"753e99bf2e1cf7fd7989861fc010a8c025352aa5","tid":105153,"uid":81805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T14:51:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用念力令到股價大升 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實唔難"},{"pid":"1cef9cc390953556b1b9255cce2623146005420e","tid":105153,"uid":11283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T16:36:36.000Z","msg":"咪玩啦，大股先令人輸得多，成班人以為大股就唔怕，不肯止蝕<br />\n相反細價股，唔包括老千股，大家都會就住就住，set 曬價位做人<br />\n做下TA 再開post 都唔遲"},{"pid":"53210a373b1641ba7ccfa28413caf3c64bb3a930","tid":105153,"uid":5419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T02:05:16.000Z","msg":"靠信念食得飽人？"},{"pid":"69c2597d5303290ab3dfa7075e0e423b08e7848f","tid":105153,"uid":81805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T05:04:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咪玩啦，大股先令人輸得多，成班人以為大股就唔怕，不肯止蝕<br />\n相反細價股，唔包括老千股，大家都會就住就住，set 曬價位做人<br />\n做下TA 再開post 都唔遲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本人認為炒股票風險一定是有的，細價股當然是好，例如一隻0.5 的股票，上落一個價位已經2%，回報非常好觀。但是細價股往往難以令人嚴守止蝕位： <br />\n1. 往往跌既時候，多數人覺得是莊家震倉。<br />\n2. 當夢醒過後，發現唔係莊家震倉，價錢已經低過止蝕價好多。<br />\n3. 細股流通量少，很容易被人造市。<br />\n4. 細價股往往沒有穩定的派息，有些更是沒有業績。<br />\n<br />\n當然有些細價股好，例如323 馬鋼， 本人看到都會跟手入一轉。 但本人喜歡推介一些有穩定派息的股票，至少唔爆升至少都可以慢慢等加埋有息落袋。<br />\n<br />\n通常本人介紹既股票，是基本面好的股票，而且經過一些基本的分析。不用擔心是8號仔，330 等的股票。 本人堅持這些股票只要有信念，股價就會自然升上合理價錢，例如80蚊買入中國移動..."},{"pid":"57c6798288880485dedda075ce19e9e502046fcc","tid":105153,"uid":81805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T05:05:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>靠信念食得飽人？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實本人喜歡用信念一言去包裝自己推介的股票已而. 本人已經分析了291 華潤啤酒的基本面。"},{"pid":"f5ff1067687efa147bce4a4e042407b3ae9ebc79","tid":105153,"uid":81805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T05:08:48.000Z","msg":"下星期既信念推介有兩隻股票，希望大家可以用信念戰勝大市。<br />\n2319 蒙牛乳業 （現價可入）<br />\n3888 金山軟件（企穩16.25 就入）"},{"pid":"4aa4a007c94eb07fb682961ab3e88cd2224409ec","tid":105153,"uid":81805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T10:35:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下星期既信念推介有兩隻股票，希望大家可以用信念戰勝大市。<br />\n2319 蒙牛乳業 （現價可入）<br />\n3888 金山軟件（企穩16.25 就入）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n推"},{"pid":"34eea34852b49879c7e549f1124fbf303bacadf7","tid":105153,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T10:59:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>靠信念食得飽人？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實本人喜歡用信念一言去包裝自己推介的股票已而. 本人已經分析了291 華潤啤酒的基本面。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n願閒其詳"},{"pid":"49b6ef37dafc047cf43d9467bc746876688b5e39","tid":105153,"uid":76855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T11:18:12.000Z","msg":"信念型投資 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif